# .trivyignore
# Path Traversal in jaraco.context (vendored in setuptools).
# Not exploitable in Veritensor CLI context as setuptools is a build dependency.

# False Positive: Vulnerability only affects Docker CLI on Windows. Our container is Linux-based.
CVE-2025-15558

# Not Exploitable: gRPC authorization bypass affects servers. Cosign acts only as a gRPC client.
CVE-2026-33186

# Not Exploitable: PATH hijacking requires existing shell access to modify environment variables.
CVE-2026-24051
CVE-2026-39883

# Accepted Risk: DoS via crafted JWE. Cosign only processes our own trusted signatures in CI/CD.
CVE-2026-34986
